3:
Someone is shouting,\q1 "In the desert plain make the way straight for Yahweh to come to you;
\q2 make a smooth road for our God.
\q1

31:
But those who trust in Yahweh will become strong again;\q2 it will be as though they will soar as eagles do.
\q1 They will run for a long time and not become weary;
\q2 they will walk long distances and not faint.
